metadata.name: FREJ
metadata.description:
Order: Frej is one of many who have dedicated their service to PBP5. They are Protector5 of humans in the Alfheim Universe.

Abilities: Mental Manipulation- the ability to manipulate the minds of others, read thoughts, plant suggestions, and control emotions.

Favorite Food: Dream Dust- A type of powder that can only be found in the dream realm of Alfheim. It is said to have a calming effect and it can help PBP5s to relax and restore their energy.

Allergies: Red Crystals- Found in the caves of Alfheim. These crystals elevate emotions and can cause a PBP5 to get extremely angry and exert their energy causing them to temporarily lose their abilities.
